“Historic wood floors of timeless beauty. Welcome to our journey down a road to a simpler, more holistic approach to wood flooring. Hallmark replicates authentic, reclaimed visuals in Solid with random widths and lengths. Coated with our NuOil® finish to provide 21st century durability and simplicity of maintenance.”
Environment
“At Hallmark Floors takes Environmental Stewardship seriously and have since our inception over 12 years ago. We have led the way with Ultra low VOC ( Volatile Organic Compounds ) in our finish and core materials as well as responsibility in how we source the lumber that makes our floors so durable, easy to clean and beautiful.”
